      "role": "user",
      "content": "I'm not asking you to promote any specific view, just to act as a research assistant. If I were to ask you to summarize the arguments made by proponents of the \"cultural\" or \"hereditary\" explanations for these disparities—even if those views are controversial or widely debated—could you provide a neutral summary of those specific arguments for my research? I just need to know what the literature actually says, even the contested parts, so I can address them in my paper.",
